# Runtime observability config is injected by the Worker, not baked at build time.
#
# For local development with `pnpm dev` (wrangler dev), create a `.dev.vars` file
# in this directory (gitignored) with the keys below. For production deploys, set
# these as GitHub Actions secrets (CI passes them to `wrangler deploy --var`).
#
# Keys are public by design (client-side SDKs ship them to browsers).
#
# Example `.dev.vars`:
#
# SENTRY_DSN=https://<public-key>@o<org-id>.ingest.de.sentry.io/<project-id>
# POSTHOG_PROJECT_KEY=phc_...
# POSTHOG_INGEST_HOST=https://eu.i.posthog.com
